<!-- ABOUT -->
<section id="about">
    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <h3>History</h3>
    <p>Sierra Football Agency was established to support talented footballers across Sierra Leone and West Africa. The agency began with a mission to identify young, skilled players and connect them with professional opportunities locally and internationally. Over the years it has grown into a leading institution in player development, carrer management, football promotion.</p>
    <p>SFA develops and represents young football talent across Sierra Leone.</p>
    <h3>Mission</h3>
    <p>Our mission is to discover, develop, and empower football talents by providing professional guidance, carrer support, and international exposure. We aim to help players unlock their full potential and achieve long term success both on and off the field.</p>
    <h3>Vision</h3>
    <p>Our vision is to become the leading football agency in Africa, recognized for players excellence in player development, transparency, and professionalism. We aim to build a future where every talented footballer has the opportunity to shine on the global stage</p>
</section>

